# Documentation Standards

- Use generic terms (work/personal) instead of specific company names (MyCompany, etc.) in documentation and examples
- Keep examples reusable: use placeholders like `work-account`, `personal-account` instead of real usernames
- Company-specific values belong in config files, not in docs
